overview.en: It is a digital asset developed based on block chain technology Use a decentralized consensus approach to build a trusted trading network for a wide range of users businesses and consumers. Investment in tourism real estate old-age care film agriculture artificial intelligence medical and health care scientific and technological innovation consumer Internet and other industries.Serve the ecological development of APH
overview.zh: 亚太坊（Asia Pacific Holding）是一种基于区块链技术开发的数字化资产，并使用去中心化的共识方式为广大的用户、商家、消费者建立一个可信任的交易网络，并基于APH 建立了亚太坊基金会，在旅游、地产、养老、电影、农业、人工智能、医疗健康、科技创新、消费互联网等各个行业作出投资，为APH 的生态发展作出服务。
